  <name>Filmbook</name>
  <summary>Track analog film usage in cameras</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Filmbook is a simple application for tracking analog film usage in cameras.
      Keep track of which films are loaded in which cameras, when they were loaded,
      and their development status.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Manage multiple cameras and film types</li>
      <li>Track loading and unloading dates</li>
      <li>Monitor development status</li>
      <li>View comprehensive film history</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

